I will help you, despite your snarkiness :)<p>Just use greasemonkey or tampermonkey and a script like this:<p><pre><code>    var a = document.getElementsByTagName(&quot;a&quot;); 
    for (i=0;i<a.length;i++) { 
        if (a[i].target=&quot;_blank&quot;) { 
            a[i].target=&quot;_self&quot; 
        }                        
    }
</code></pre>
It should work for the majority of cases.  You should be able to tweak it to handle any exceptions.
